data.enText: a French sparkling white wine (= one with bubbles) that is drunk on special occasions

tr: a white sparkling wine either produced in Champagne or resembling that produced there

value.def: Champagne is an expensive French white wine with bubbles in. It is often drunk to celebrate something.
If you say that champagne corks are popping, you mean that people are celebrating something.

trans: 香槟粉；粉香槟；粉红香槟
